data.description:
Seller is offering to cover fees to permanently buy down interest rate to 6.25% with a preferred lender using an FHA loan with a full price offer. 

Introducing 242 Hickory Grove Church Rd in Sumrall, MS! This spacious 5-bed, 3-bath home boasts an open floor plan with custom brick floors, concrete, and granite countertops, a large pantry, and home office space. Enjoy the luxury of custom-built cabinetry, walk-in closets, and 2493 sq ft of living space. The property features a spacious 2-car garage, plus a golf cart garage and a large attic which are all heated/cooled. Don't worry about the power bill because the home is fully spray foam insulated. Situated atop a hill on a picturesque 3.13 acre lot with a large barn out back for all of your toys and additional storage requirements. Call your agent to schedule your showing and prepare to fall in Love!!
